snippet.title: HUGE Win For Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
HUGE Win For Johnny Depp
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

A judge has officially denied Amber Heard’s request to dismiss the case against her, which means the 50 million dollar defamation lawsuit is going ahead as planned. This is a huge win for Johnny Depp, it means that the judge thinks that there is enough evidence and testimony to proceed. I’m going to serve you this update, right now on IO.
